dct_description_sm: Published at Washington, D.C. August 1911 by the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey ; O. H. Tittman, Superintendent.
Depths shown by soundings, lines, spot shading; relief shown by contours.
Includes various correction informatino, with dates between 1851 and 1911.
Shows lights, beacons, buoys, city plans, railroads, waterways.
